                                                      Book News, Inc., 12/01/95:<br>
                                                      A fascinating memoir providing insight into the Agency's<br>
                                                      extensive covert operations in northern Laos while<br>
                                                      recounting Parker's personal experiences as an American<br>
                                                      officer who was immersed in Southeast Asian culture.<br>
